@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

title System Sequence Diagram (SSD) - Alternative One

autonumber

actor "Green Space Manager" as Employee
participant ":System" as System


activate Employee

    Employee -> System : ask to register a green space
    activate System

        System --> Employee : request data (name,area,address)
    deactivate System

    Employee -> System : types requested data


    activate System

            System --> Employee : shows list of sizes option\n and request a selection
        deactivate System

        Employee -> System : select an option



    activate System

        System --> Employee : show all data registered\n and the confirmation menu
    deactivate System

    Employee -> System : submits data
    activate System

        System --> Employee : shows operation (in)success
    deactivate System

@enduml